    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Use this method to create hard links between files in the current file system. If "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "srcPath"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " is a directory, this method creates a new directory at "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "dstPath"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and then creates hard links for the items in that directory. If "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "srcPath"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " is (or contains) a symbolic link, the symbolic link is copied to the new location and not converted to a hard link."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Prior to linking each item, the file manager asks its delegate if it should actually create the link. It does this by calling the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/nsfilemanagerdelegate/1417589-filemanager"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method; if that method is not implemented it calls the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/nsfilemanagerdelegate/1414699-filemanager"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method instead. If the delegate method returns "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/yes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", or if the delegate does not implement the appropriate methods, the file manager creates the hard link. If there is an error linking one out of several items, the file manager may also call the delegateâ€™s "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/nsfilemanagerdelegate/1408003-filemanager"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " or "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/nsfilemanagerdelegate/1415627-filemanager"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method to determine how to proceed."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
